Mobile Python IDE for Nokia S60 platform.

Ped is a mobile application created using Nokia's Python port for the S60 mobile platform (<span style="color:#00ff00;"><a style="color:#00ff00;" href="https://garage.maemo.org/frs/?group_id=854" rel="nofollow">PyS60</a></span>). It is a text editor focused on writing, executing and debugging Python code directly on the mobile device. Additional features like comfortable built-in Python Shell make it a true mobile Python IDE. Check out the screenshots and see for yourself

Using this,we can write  and run PyS60 scripts on cellphone itself.

Download: <span style="color:#00ff00;"><a style="color:#00ff00;" href="https://code.google.com/p/ped-s60/downloads/list">PED</a></span>

It requires PyS60.

